data.description: This delightful 3-bed, 3-bath residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and style for everyone. This home has been meticulously maintained, with thoughtful updates. The well-designed layout of this home makes it an ideal space for entertaining, both indoors and out. The cathedral ceilings in the living room add an element of grandeur, the electric fireplace creating a warm and inviting ambiance for gatherings. Enjoy the convenience of central air conditioning throughout the home, ensuring a comfortable environment year-round. With a finished basement boasting in-law-rental potential, this home is providing flex living. The recently updated bathrooms featuring modern fixtures. Benefit from abundant natural light through the newer windows. With Craigville Beach & Lake Wequaquet in close proximity, outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the easy access to various water activities. Explore the possibility of future development to suit your needs. You don't want to miss this.
